835. mediam metam, ‘the central goal’, is of course the centre simply: the word perhaps suggested (as C. says) by the double race course, where the meta was the post in the centre round which they had to go. (C.’s own int. that meta is the ‘apex of the cone’ and so the top of the sky, is less suitable.)
